@BookTracker.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5202

GET {{BookTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json



###

GET {{BookTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/books
Accept: application/json

### Create Book
POST http://localhost:5202/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dune",
  "author": "Frank Herbert",
  "year": 1965
}

### Delete Book
DELETE http://localhost:5202/books/1 

### Delete Book (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:5202/books/9999